title: Good Earth Organic Eatery
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Italian, Macrobiotic, Organic, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegan except for fish, established 2012 by an Italian-born owner and chef. Vegan suitable items include the daily macrobiotic plate with whole grain dish, cooked veggies, beans, and salad; vegan pasta and risotto; sandwiches; salads and soups. Drinks include fresh-squeezed juices, wheatgrass juice, iced and hot teas, house-made almond milk, and barley coffee. Has gluten-free, house-made bread (without dairy, sugar, egg). BYOB. ATM machine inside.
